Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊  熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.71,0:00:29.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.71,0:00:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會吧  你把葡萄果醬全部吃光了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難得千影姐做給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是愛吃也不能吃太多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:45.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是一直都在強調著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣不是和小鈴姐一提到紅豆大福一樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.80,0:02:33.80,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,尋找熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我很喜歡紅豆大福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.98,0:02:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我也很喜歡燒魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:53.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來到這島上已經幾天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,家裡一定鬧翻天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.86,0:03:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的要一直在這個島上生活下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.95,0:03:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊呀  雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人都振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  那邊就交給你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話  只有用最後的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.89,0:03:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這回可要好好完成人工呼吸…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  醒過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  幸虧醒過來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家由於擔心雪乃而聚集起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:11.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太專注摘葡萄了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結果腳下打滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們擔心了  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不用特意摔到別人的身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大家都把雪乃當作自己的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:35.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  要說的話  我就像大家的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真會說好話  小貓頭鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我們也會有這種感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼感覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我稍微能有些察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.46,0:05:05.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩人都聽得懂動物的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人不懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  一般來說都不懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:14.51,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（你不能和動物交談嗎）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:19.03,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（讀寫算是基本哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.42,0:05:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  等等…怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.13,0:05:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是什麼傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  熊熊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  剛才還一起摘葡萄的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一般來說熊熊肯定會第一個衝出來救雪乃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:31.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.40,0:05:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子很貪吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定在附近閒逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  來幫忙尋找熊熊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  為什麼我要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.54,0:05:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.78,0:05:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就在這裡分為兩隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是  那樣效率會比較高吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:55.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我和行人找這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴姐和大家去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.78,0:06:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明顯人數很不平衡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.97,0:06:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.06,0:06:07.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:10.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.29,0:06:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,約會啦  約會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道約會的意思嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.53,0:06:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,確實剛才在這附近還和熊熊在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.90,0:06:26.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  稍微注意點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.28,0:06:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,淑女的臉受傷了該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.07,0:06:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來你自己走不就好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:42.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是腳印嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  難道是熊熊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛  只要跟著腳印很快就能找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.41,0:06:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.64,0:06:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  普通都會注意到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.98,0:06:58.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:06:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真好  雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.97,0:07:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼快找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.97,0:07:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是熊熊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為熊熊是和我差不多年齡的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和這種大叔完全不同的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.23,0:07:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是怎麼看都和熊熊一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為…為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是行人一直盯著看才生氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:38.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這腳印原來是那大叔的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好難分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.34,0:07:42.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺食慾很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是和麻知姐一樣年齡的男生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:58.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那這傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不像女孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊的臉更圓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:06.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起漂亮系不如說是可愛系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.28,0:08:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮系？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:10.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…這個嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然看上去外表很像女生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:17.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但仔細看  就會發覺其實是女生臉的美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美少…年？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡面的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊是這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  大家無論年齡  臉  外形都完全和熊熊不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼就不明白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼會明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到居然會有那麼多熊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:49.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:51.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都說沒有見到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.02,0:08:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,胸部有彎月牙花紋的熊很少見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:56.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:59.00,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.07,0:09:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然有那麼明顯的標誌的話  為什麼不早點說…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:05.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有點累了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.57,0:09:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,休息一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明自己幾乎都沒走過什麼路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.18,0:09:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.23,0:09:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又被捲入奇怪的事情裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼這島上的女孩子們都是自我主義呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  反正我也習慣這種狀態了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:37.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我責駡熊熊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:43.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為熊熊把做好放置在那的葡萄果醬全部吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就對她說了  「不能成為像小鈴姐那樣的貪吃鬼」這樣過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這…這是過分的話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說熊熊  去哪裡鬧彆扭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  我是感覺不會因為這麼小的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.25,0:09:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然你和熊熊的關係最好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在關係好的朋友裡是不分一二的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.58,0:10:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  論交往時間的話  我和熊熊是最長的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在我還只會玩耍的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴姐她們都已經開始工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是六歲的時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在此以前我一直以為一個人玩是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.26,0:10:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自從和熊熊相遇後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:03.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像一開始去捅蜂巢呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,河裡抓鮭魚呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了擁有好身材而舒展身體
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人偷偷一起化妝等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:26.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發生了許多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都和熊熊在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,此後和許多動物的關係也處的很好…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊轉眼就長的比我大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.00,0:11:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別看她這樣  很膽小的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在也許迷路了  正為難著  在哭吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.92,0:11:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.18,0:11:54.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然裝作姐姐那樣很堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但其實一直都在擔心著熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坐立不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.73,0:12:08.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～熊熊去哪裡了～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼突然  幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有空哭的話  還不如抓緊去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.92,0:12:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刺刺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不應該在這個世界上存在的邪惡的殺氣？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「不應該在這個世界上存在的邪惡的殺氣」是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是指那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.72,0:13:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.77,0:13:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們在這裡已經百年不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是每天都見面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.06,0:13:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  那邊的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.57,0:13:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「不應該在這個世界上存在的邪惡的殺氣」是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  我就當作是誇獎的話心存感激地收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.83,0:13:52.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈哈哈～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾音就是這樣一個傻到腦筋大條的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:00.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們  都不要出手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我和鈴之間冤家路窄的決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.99,0:14:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在很忙  等下再陪你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊  這居高臨下的口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我這連眼睛都無法捕捉到的快速移動的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的動作太多了  綾音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.72,0:14:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃一直都像這樣被大家保護著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.44,0:14:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炸豬排也保護著我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  行人也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢  小貓頭鷹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:59.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人他並不是在保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  行人畫的好糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在是發表感歎的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:34.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喏  和熊熊很像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.13,0:15:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這要怎麼做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:50.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  請問這只熊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.02,0:15:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這麼突然…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個島上是沒有男孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以第一次看到行人的話  就連熊也會吃驚的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,衡  這樣變裝就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:07.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請問這只熊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  還以為動物很容易親近…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.08,0:16:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣打扮的話  不就更可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.25,0:16:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然熊熊生我的氣了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  居然這麼難找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:22.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是離家出走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想找到熊熊就是絕對不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛才說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:32.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是離家出走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.11,0:16:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.90,0:16:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「絕對不行」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:41.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,世上絕對沒有「絕對不行」的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…也許不能說「絕對」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:48.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  這樣想的我  已經輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺說過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果自己都不相信自己的力量  怎麼能行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:16:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:16:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃  交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.07,0:17:02.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對找出熊熊給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是可疑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個不是武器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是畫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無視我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.08,0:17:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.64,0:17:16.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是畫的熊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你們的…朋•友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夥•伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是這隻熊的朋•友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.65,0:17:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到此為止都還OK？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:38.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你都幹了些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我難得畫的肖像畫都白費了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,問小動物的話  就不會打飛了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這畫也許不是很像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:57.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但這裡有像月牙一樣的標誌…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是個名叫熊熊的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,年齡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和雪乃一樣11歲左右…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.91,0:18:17.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說漂亮系  還不如是可愛系的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.07,0:18:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:27.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃  這位大叔說在那邊看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.74,0:18:32.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.19,0:18:36.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那個就當作回禮給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.13,0:18:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點  行行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…「行行」是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊好像沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該就在那橋對面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:57.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:18:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是不是有點太高了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.51,0:19:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  行人對高處不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我一個人去好了  等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:15.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  雪乃  跑著是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人把我帶到這裡了  我也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  橋塌了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.79,0:19:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人——！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:39.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  千鈞一髮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要道謝的話  還早了點吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.22,0:20:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  倒過來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.61,0:20:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.43,0:20:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  讓人那麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雪乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,熊熊～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:24.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:25.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到熊熊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們很擔心  一直尋找著你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.29,0:20:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,結果是互相在找對方  而迷路了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還一直以為熊熊離家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有那種可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:47.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧  雪乃  如她所說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.67,0:20:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  你從剛才就能聽懂熊熊的話了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  說起來  我能和動物交流了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是麼  是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:21:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是習慣這島的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.49,0:21:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天開始行行也是我們的伙伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教  行行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:09.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  不要啦  我才不想習慣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行行…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:46.99,biaoti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\3c&HE7A573}暖和的溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.10,0:22:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.16,0:23:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是最親近的炸豬排的話  還是除了「噗」以外什麼都聽不出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  炸豬排的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.64,0:23:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,連我也只能聽懂「噗」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.09,0:23:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.09,0:23:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.84,0:23:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.45,0:23:24.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.83,0:23:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.56,0:23:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.11,0:23:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,溺水了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.62,0:23:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  這回一定要好好地做——人工呼吸！
